channel.title: Need desperate help getting into servers
channel.description: Well last night I was on a server and it was great fun I loved it ;) But today I can't join anything all i get is "Error connecting to server. Must be down. Set up ur own etc" My friend was in the same server that I was trying to get into and he said it was fine. Any help would be greatly appreciated. Cheers!
